      <title>韩国代理领导人无视尹某审判法官的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/korea-s-acting-leader-refuses-to-appoint-judges-for-yoon-s-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国代理总统韩德洙不顾反对派压力，批准任命法官，此举可能增加罢免总统尹锡烈权力的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/korea-s-acting-leader-refuses-to-appoint-judges-for-yoon-s-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 04:57:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受制裁的俄罗斯液化天然气船寻求买家四个月仍未成功</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/sanctioned-russian-lng-ship-fails-four-month-quest-for-buyer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘载有受制裁的俄罗斯液化天然气的船只似乎正在将其卸载到俄罗斯远东地区的仓库，尽管经过四个月的环球航行，却未能找到愿意规避美国限制的买家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/sanctioned-russian-lng-ship-fails-four-month-quest-for-buyer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 04:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾前总统候选人柯文哲因贪污被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/former-taiwan-presidential-candidate-ko-indicted-for-corruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾前总统候选人柯文哲因担任台北市长期间涉及多起腐败丑闻而被起诉，其中包括一项房地产重建项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/former-taiwan-presidential-candidate-ko-indicted-for-corruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 03:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平扩大国防清洗，中国罢免两名军方议员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/china-ousts-two-military-lawmakers-as-xi-s-defense-purge-widens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国突然在没有任何解释的情况下将两名军事立法者从全国人大中罢免，而国防高层关键人员的清洗行动也丝毫没有缓和的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/china-ousts-two-military-lawmakers-as-xi-s-defense-purge-widens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 02:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本计划增加国防开支 预算创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/japan-to-unveil-record-budget-with-ramped-up-defense-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相石破茂的内阁预计将于周五批准下一财年的创纪录初始预算，这将增加国防开支和对地方经济的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/japan-to-unveil-record-budget-with-ramped-up-defense-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 01:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据俄新社报道，俄罗斯称军用货船沉没系恐怖袭击所致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/russia-says-terrorist-attack-behind-army-cargo-ship-sinking-ria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国家通讯社俄新社援引船主的话报道，本周在地中海沉没的一艘俄罗斯军用货船成为恐怖袭击的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/russia-says-terrorist-attack-behind-army-cargo-ship-sinking-ria</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 16:22:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日中同意北京高级外交官于 2025 年访日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/japan-china-agree-to-visit-by-beijing-s-top-diplomat-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和日本同意北京的最高外交官于 2025 年访日，这进一步表明两国正在修复近年来紧张的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/japan-china-agree-to-visit-by-beijing-s-top-diplomat-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 09:09:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克选举危机升级 陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/mozambique-death-and-looting-rock-nation-in-wake-of-disputed-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在去年 10 月有争议的选举中，执政党的胜利被确认后，莫桑比克各地爆发了暴力事件，导致本周至少 89 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/mozambique-death-and-looting-rock-nation-in-wake-of-disputed-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 06:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯在圣诞节袭击乌克兰能源网络</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/ukraine-limits-power-supplies-amid-russian-attack-at-christmas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯对乌克兰能源基础设施发动大规模导弹袭击，导致该国电网运营商在圣诞节当天限制电力供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/ukraine-limits-power-supplies-amid-russian-attack-at-christmas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 06:15:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国为何清洗部分高级军事领导人？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/china-military-purge-what-we-know-about-corruption-allegations-xi-s-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平已投入数十亿美元，希望到 2027 年将军队改造成一支现代化军队。美国情报部门认为，中国人民解放军高层普遍存在腐败现象，破坏了习近平的宏伟目标。中国政府还对中国人民解放军高层进行了大规模清洗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/china-military-purge-what-we-know-about-corruption-allegations-xi-s-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 09:27:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
